      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "VIRESHA (4) missed first-up in a stronger race but just missed over this track and trip in a Class 1 last time. Third-up now and she's a third-up winner in the past. Wouldn't surprise to see her go one better again today. CALL ME FROSTY (1) comes here looking for the hat-trick after a dominant win over 1200m last time. Li's claim gets him in light at the weights and he'll no doubt be up front from the outset. Rates highly once again and can extend the streak. I'M GENEVIEVE (6) was plain fresh but improved well last start when flying late to finish 0.2L off the winner. Back to 1100m now, but she is a winner at this track and trip prior. Nottle hops on board and she can strike third-up into the campaign. DEEPLY ROOTED (5) is better than he showed last start and won't be far away.",
